section.para:
The plugin defines a new packaging type and so you must ensure that extensions is set to true in your plugin declaration:
Adding the plugin to a project <project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0"> // project header...
<build> <!-- To define the plugin version in your parent POM --> <pluginManagement> <plugins> <plugin> <groupId></groupId> <artifactId></artifactId> <version></version> <extensions>true</extensions> </plugin>
// other plugins... </plugins> </pluginManagement> <!-- To use the plugin goals in your POM or parent POM --> <plugins> <plugin> <groupId></groupId> <artifactId></artifactId> <version></version> <extensions>true</extensions> </plugin>
// other plugins... </plugins> </build>
// rest of project config... </project>
